2.0.0 (xx/xx/2022)
- Reworked categories. Now many categories with few modifiers in each, rather than few categories with many modifiers. Allows for more fine-grained randomisation
- Added Legendary Nerf feature
- Added feature to allow buff/nerf to be rerolled for a country when a new leader takes over a country
- Allowed buffs/nerfs for Pirates, Rebels, and Natives (for some categories)
- Refactored the randomizer code significantly
- Reworked the Settings Menu to make more sense
- Different chances for Player vs. AI for categories (VERY rare for players to get L3 buffs/nerfs)
- Optional different max tiers for players vs. AI (i.e. players can get a range from N1 - B1, while AI get LN - LB)
- Rebalance of most everything

1.1.3 (05/01/2022)
- Corrected missing title/description for the new decision in 1.1.2
- Fixed Continental Legendary Country system
- Corrected some grammer in the settings menu
- Made some menu items easier to use
- Made it so that the decision to reroll the buffs/nerfs is actually randomized

1.1.2 (04/01/2022)
- Added decision to allow viewing of legendary countries

1.1.1 (22/12/2021)
- made sure to clear player modifiers always (if needed :) )
- added ability to change settings mid-game

1.1.0 (20/12/2021)
- upgraded to EU4 1.32
- added per-continent legendary countries
- configurable chance for legendary nations
- added Court and Trade categories
- small change to Economy category
- added some extra presets

1.0.5 (12/03/2021)
- Removed screenshots, steam_desc, and version_history files from the mod directory.

1.0.4 (11/03/2021)
- Updated steam description and started towards adding a detailed revision history.
- Added decision to allow rerolling buffs/nerfs (unequal_nations_reroll_nations). This can be used at any time, will likely go through changes/restrictions in the future (not too heavily tested right now).

1.0.3 (11/12/2020)
- Fixed issue causing age changing to constantly update buffs/nerfs.

1.0.2 (08/12/2020)
 - Setting menu linking fix.

1.0.1 (08/12/2020)
 - Minor localization fixes.

1.0.0 (08/12/2020)
 - Initial release.
